eNCA's Dasen Thathiah has more details on this story. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Umgeni Water says it will be hiring contractors to take care of the water infrastructure issues affecting residents in Hillcrest in Durban. The water services authority visited the area on Monday. READ: Water supply reduction in parts of Joburg Some areas have been without water since the floods in Kwazulu-Natal. One family had a supply pipe fall on top of their home.